<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idcb275321-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70" identifier="/us/usc/t49/s22906"><num value="22906">§ 22906.</num><heading> Authorization of appropriations</heading>
<chapeau style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There are authorized to be appropriated to the Secretary of Transportation for capital grants under this chapter the following amounts:</chapeau><paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="idcb275322-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70" identifier="/us/usc/t49/s22906/1"><num value="1">(1)</num><content> For fiscal year 2009, $100,000,000.</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="idcb275323-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70" identifier="/us/usc/t49/s22906/2"><num value="2">(2)</num><content> For fiscal year 2010, $300,000,000.</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="idcb275324-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70" identifier="/us/usc/t49/s22906/3"><num value="3">(3)</num><content> For fiscal year 2011, $400,000,000.</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="idcb275325-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70" identifier="/us/usc/t49/s22906/4"><num value="4">(4)</num><content> For fiscal year 2012, $500,000,000.</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="idcb275326-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70" identifier="/us/usc/t49/s22906/5"><num value="5">(5)</num><content> For fiscal year 2013, $600,000,000.</content>
</paragraph>
<sourceCredit id="idcb275327-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70">(Added <ref href="/us/pl/110/432/dB/tIII/s301/a">Pub. L. 110–432, div. B, title III, § 301(a)</ref>, <date date="2008-10-16">Oct. 16, 2008</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/122/4946">122 Stat. 4946</ref>, § 24406; renumbered § 22906, <ref href="/us/pl/115/420/s7/a/1">Pub. L. 115–420, § 7(a)(1)</ref>, <date date="2019-01-03">Jan. 3, 2019</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/132/5445">132 Stat. 5445</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
